Alembic async migration environment for the Hotel Management System API.

The database URL is read from app settings (DATABASE_URL) in env.py, so you do
not need to set sqlalchemy.url in alembic.ini.

Common commands:
  alembic revision --autogenerate -m "init"   # generate a migration
  alembic upgrade head                         # apply migrations
  alembic downgrade -1                         # roll back one revision
